  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I've updated the patch set to include minimal changes to the weekly e-mail to use this 
receive_maintainer_updates feature.

This temporarily means only maintainers will receive weekly e-mails. I think this is fine, because 
ultimately we'll want distinct content for maintainers and contributors/iwannahelpers anyway.

I am unable to test the weekly e-mail sending facilities in my environment right now. I'd 
appreciate them getting tested by someone before this gets pushed live if these changes are going 
to be shipped tonight for the milestone.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
